      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "ADOBE MARKETO ENGAGE\nPowerful marketing automation.\n\nMarketo Engage is a complete AI-powered marketing automation platform that helps teams scale personalized buyer engagement and grow predictable pipeline and revenue. Attract the right buyers, nurture them across channels and journeys, keep sales and marketing in sync, and deliver insights that maximize marketing impact on revenue.\n\nWatch overview\nBook a demo"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 329,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Explore the features of Marketo Engage.\n\nMarketo Engage is a central hub where you can plan, execute, and measure omnichannel campaigns — from batch email campaigns to automated nurture to advanced multi-step campaigns. Built from the ground up to be secure, support compliance, and easily connect to other applications, it powers marketing and sales team success at every maturity level."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section tablist-features-section",
      "height": 622,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "AI and agentic capabilities\nCampaign operations\nOmnichannel engagement\nPersonalized content\nSales intelligence & engagement\nMarketing analytics\nProfiles & audiences\nPut AI to work in your daily workflows.\n\nCreate content faster, optimize journeys, onboard teams, and automate marketing operations tasks with AI.\n\nGenerate email copy, subject lines, and Firefly-powered images — all within Marketo Engage.\nAutomate repetitive marketing operations work, such as creating templates, cleaning imported lists, enforcing data governance, and validating assets. *\nQuickly create, analyze, and optimize multi"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "tag": "div",
