      "textPreview": "Put AI to work in your daily workflows.\n\nCreate content faster, optimize journeys, onboard teams, and automate marketing operations tasks with AI.\n\nGenerate email copy, subject lines, and Firefly-powered images — all within Marketo Engage.\nAutomate repetitive marketing operations work, such as creating templates, cleaning imported lists, enforcing data governance, and validating assets. *\nQuickly create, analyze, and optimize multitouch journeys at scale. *\nHelp Marketo Engage users quickly discover and use features with an AI assistant that answers “How to” questions with easy step-by-step gu"
    },
